可以帮助他人进入该校」等问题。随后，梁某短视频账号被封禁。 作为新兴的社会群体，网红主播因其鲜明的特点和广泛影响力，受到粉丝的追捧和信任。大厂高管、创业导师、名校毕业生…当主播们顶着高学历「光环」，讲述个人丰富多彩的故事时，背后却可能是为了引流变现而事先设计好的「爽文」剧本，一旦塌房，不仅辜负网友的信任，也是对社会诚信体系的挑衅。同时，造假带来的市场竞争机制扭曲，还将让整个行业陷入信任危机。 在网络空间，学历并不是衡量作品的唯一标准。不少网红主播就曾在直播中回应网友关于其学历、经历的问题，虽然没有光鲜靓丽的学历和阅历，但普通人的奋斗故事同样能收获大量粉丝。用诚信、真诚赢得的关注和粉丝，远比虚构人设来得更牢靠。千万网红被指学历造假，诚信比人设更重要"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dfea286a2a5506f0c550fa9a79381461_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "145 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/921058235"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+/SgpLjooPV/EAMaCTExMTE1ODcyOSCP07a4BjAAOFxABXIJOTIxMDU4MjM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1728987153.163227", "card_id": "Q_927190316", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024 年 Steam 新品节已开始，哪款新游会是你心中的白月光呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "感觉新游戏太多了，求推荐一些好玩的 demo 试玩"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-95805931e811ae0e68a90f709bd48bd8_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "107 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/927190316"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+/SgpLjooPV/EAMaCTExMTE2MTIzOCDMqre4BjAAOFJABnIJOTI3MTkwMzE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1728987153.163515", "card_id": "Q_869861366", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87